-- Turkish Airlines to Expand U.S. Coverage With Flights to Houston
-- B y   B e n j a m i n   H a r v e y
-- 2012-06-18T08:35:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-18/turkish-airlines-to-expand-u-s-coverage-with-flights-to-houston.html
Turk Hava Yollari AO, the carrier
known as Turkish Airlines, will begin direct flights to Houston
four days a week starting in April of next year, the company
said in an e-mailed statement today.  Turkish Airlines currently flies direct to Chicago,  Los
Angeles , New York and Washington from Istanbul, according to the
statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Benjamin Harvey in Istanbul at 
 bharvey11@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
